
How to install the library
--------------------------


Building the library
-------------------

First, build the content of the lib/ directory using the command:

make

This will create the shared library. In this case, it will create
the .so version file and a soft link file.

Using the library with an application
--------------------------------------

The examples/ directory contains an application that tests the library.

Building the application
------------------------

To build the application use the command:

make

This will generate the file mcp3008_raspi_test.bin in the same directory.

Executig the test application
-----------------------------

And now run it with admin permissions:

sudo ./mcp3008_raspi_test.bin

